T1  - Size of investment, opportunity choice and human resources in new venture growth: Some typologies
AU  - Thakur, Sanjay Prasad
JO  - Journal of Business Venturing
VL  - 14
IS  - 3
SP  - 283
EP  - 309
PY  - 1999
DA  - 1999/05/01/
